Sentencas: Strontium doped lanthanum manganite ((La0.85Sr0.15)(0.98)MnO3; LSM)/yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) nanocomposite particles were synthesized through a novel co-precipitation method using YSZ nanoparticles with the average size of 3 unit as seed crystals.
Titulo: Novel co-precipitation derived nanostructured LSM-YSZ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Phase evolution studies indicated that crystalline LSM/YSZ phases were obtained by calcining the co-precipitated precursor above 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Novel co-precipitation derived nanostructured LSM-YSZ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The nanocomposite particles calcined at 1000 degrees C were screen printed on YSZ dense electrolytes and then sintered at 1100 degrees C for cathode fabrication.
Titulo: Novel co-precipitation derived nanostructured LSM-YSZ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The resulting cathode had a uniform porous structure consisting of fine grains similar to 100 nm in size, and exhibited low polarization resistance of 2.82, 1.18, 0.48 and 0.25 Omega.cm(2) at 650, 700, 750 and 800 degrees C, respectively under air atmosphere.
Titulo: Novel co-precipitation derived nanostructured LSM-YSZ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results indicated that the present nanostructured cathode may be applicable for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Novel co-precipitation derived nanostructured LSM-YSZ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
